title: Egypt's Ex-Military Chief Right For Presidency, Female Voter Says
teaser: Egyptians elect a new president next week. There are two candidates, and the man nearly certain to win is Abdel Fattah al-Sisi. He was the head of the military until he resigned to run for president.
